{"type":null,"faqId":33966,"title":"为何无法唤醒手机/唤醒率很低？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">首先确认下是否打开了语音唤醒功能以及训练的唤醒词是否正确；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">其次确保唤醒词训练的时候对着MIC，以及保持训练环境安静；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">正确训练方式：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">训练的时候最好在相对安静的环境下，建议45°左右握持手机，距离20至40cm，并尽量使用日常生活中最自然的语速、语调进行训练。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">注意训练唤醒的时候不要距离MIC太近，如果太近的话容易导致破音，导致唤醒率低！</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8668","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748777000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":140,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"不能唤醒手机,不好使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}